DEUTSCHE BANK NATIONAL TRUST COMPANY, etc., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Michael HART, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2304 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017

ORDERED that appellant's notice of voluntary dismissal is recognized by the Court, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
